This Map is a tribute to the Map SF_CSAR of the game Americas Army, it isn't 1:1 but it looks like the original.
I've taken about 2 weeks to make it and i think it's very good for second map, if you find some bugs or you got a good idea tell me here or aou cant contact me on my Clan HP www.6thDD.com

I hope you like my work and maybe someone put this map on a Big Server, then we only got a small 12 slot server and I got to make some settings to let the map run on our server.

Thx @ all
